**Inflation erodes purchasing power** — a corpus of ₹1 crore in 20 years may only have the purchasing power of ₹30–35 lakhs in today's terms at 6% inflation. This calculator converts your nominal investment returns into real, inflation-adjusted returns so you can plan more accurately for future financial goals.
